                {
                    "id": "monin_obukhov_unstable",
                    "description": "Unstable surface layer: positive (upward) heat flux q_z = 100 W/m^2 with u_star = 0.4 m/s. Upstream \"Monin-Obukhov length\" test 2: L must be negative. ζ < 0 selects the Businger-Dyer unstable branch.",
