                    "description": "Stable surface layer: negative (downward) heat flux q_z = -50 W/m^2 (surface cooling). Upstream \"Monin-Obukhov length\" test 3: L must be positive. ζ > 0 selects the stable branch φ_m = φ_h = 1 + 4.7ζ.",
