                    "id": "businger_dyer_stable",
                    "description": "Businger-Dyer stability functions under stable conditions (u_star = 0.2 m/s, q_z = -50 W/m^2). Upstream \"Businger-Dyer stability functions\" test 2: ζ > 0 and φ_m = φ_h = 1 + 4.7ζ. Here 1 + 4.7·0.691123 = 4.248279.",
